      <title>当银幕与屏幕间的堑壕崩塌时</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E5%BD%93%E9%93%B6%E5%B9%95%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A0%91%E5%A3%95%E5%B4%A9%E5%A1%8C%E6%97%B6/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 May 2025 11:26:53 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E5%BD%93%E9%93%B6%E5%B9%95%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A0%91%E5%A3%95%E5%B4%A9%E5%A1%8C%E6%97%B6/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They went to sea in a Sieve, they did,
In a Sieve they went to sea:
In spite of all their friends could say,
On a winter’s morn, on a stormy day,
In a Sieve they went to sea!
Far and few, far and few,
Are the lands where the Jumblies live;
Their heads are green, and their hands are blue,
And they went to sea in a Sieve.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
